Package net.sf.mmm.client.ui.api.attribute Description

Contains abstract interfaces for common attributes of UI objects.

Client UI API Attribute

This package contains interfaces for common attributes such as ID for the client UI. These attribute interfaces helps to standardize signatures (including javadoc) and allows generic access to attributes for other utilities and libraries.
